NAME
    Dist::Zilla::Plugin::MojibakeTest - Release tests making sure no char
    encoding problems is in the code

VERSION
    version 0.001

DESCRIPTION
    This is an extension of Dist::Zilla::Plugin::InlineFiles, providing the
    following files:

    *   xt/release/mojibake.t

        a standard Test::Mojibake test

AUTHOR
    Alexei Znamensky <russoz@cpan.org>

